# Generated pipeline outputs — the whole agent-system outputs dir regenerates
# every run (review CSVs, slates, schedules, calibration, run logs, snapshots),
# producing thousands of lines of churn. The live site reads Firestore and the
# routine reads these from disk, so tracking isn't needed. Hand-authored agent
# docs live in docs/agent-system/ (PHASE_*.md, agents/) and stay tracked.
docs/agent-system/outputs/
predictions_*.json
predictions_*.md
